This project is a minimalist, content-driven personal website built with the Astro framework.

Features:
- Homepage (/)
- Blog (/blog)
- Portfolio page (/projects)
- Social media links collection (/links)

Technologies used:
- Framework: Astro
- CSS: Tailwind CSS with DaisyUI
- Markdown: MDX
- Language: TypeScript
- Package Manager: bun
- Deployment: Cloudflare Pages (Premium/paid plan, Static)

Key directories and files:

- src/components/Head.astro: HTML <head>, Astro SEO and OpenGraph stuff goes Header
- src/components/content/index.ts: Reusable content-specific components

- src/content/blog/godot/index.mdx: A post in the 'blog' content collection
- src/content/projects/smpearth/index.mdx: A project in the 'projects' content collection
- src/content/config.ts: Astro content schemas 

- src/content/icons/: Icons used by astro-icon package

- src/layouts/PageLayout.astro: Global layout

- src/lib/utils.ts: Generic helper functions

- src/pages/index.astro: Homepage
- src/pages/blog/index.astro: Blog post directory
- src/pages/blog/[...slug].astro: Blog post
- src/pages/projects/index.astro: Project post directory
- src/pages/projects/[...slug].astro: Project post
- src/pages/links/index.astro: Links page (WIP)

- src/consts.ts: Global constants
- src/env.d.ts: Global references
- src/global.css: Global stylesheet
- src/ogRenderer.tsx: OpenGraph image generator
- src/types.ts: Global types

- astro.config.mjs: Astro configuration
- eslint.config.mjs: ESLint configuration
- package.json: Project dependencies
- tailwind.config.mjs: Tailwind CSS configuration
